08:00.464 --> 08:02.530
[ Machine tapping ]

08:06.536 --> 08:08.336
Can't you just see him there,

08:08.371 --> 08:10.171
writing in his diary
every night,

08:10.206 --> 08:12.673
making his little
observations

08:12.708 --> 08:16.878
about everyone,
his parishioners, us...

08:16.913 --> 08:19.847
He should've kept it locked
in a goddamn safe.

08:19.883 --> 08:22.149
Why?
He's got God on his side.

08:22.185 --> 08:23.851
What could go wrong?

08:25.721 --> 08:29.656
Paige isn't gonna get over this
so easy.

08:29.692 --> 08:31.759
- She'll be fine.
- I don't know.

08:31.794 --> 08:33.659
This whole thing.
All of it.

08:33.696 --> 08:36.263
She's not the type of kid
who can put things behind her.

08:36.298 --> 08:38.432
[ Inhales deeply ]

08:38.467 --> 08:41.801
She's not.

08:41.836 --> 08:43.937
But it's not all bad.

08:43.972 --> 08:45.372
She's starting to see him

08:45.407 --> 08:47.173
for what he is.

