23:19.379 --> 23:20.811
Renee: Well, still.

23:20.847 --> 23:22.614
We should do
dinner again soon.

23:22.649 --> 23:24.015
Maybe next week?
That--

23:24.050 --> 23:25.617
There's that new Indian
on Sycamore.

23:25.652 --> 23:27.652
Um, I actually have
to head home next week.

23:27.687 --> 23:30.021
Oh. Yeah.
Well, the-- the week after?

23:30.056 --> 23:31.523
- For sure. - Definitely.
- Great.

23:31.558 --> 23:32.557
- Yeah.
- All right. We'll see you then.

23:32.592 --> 23:34.091
- Great. - Okay.
- Okay.

23:34.127 --> 23:35.192
- Good night. - Bye. See ya.
- Bye. Good night.

23:35.227 --> 23:36.593
[ Inhales sharply ]

23:36.629 --> 23:38.929
